              <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM1325506">Section 26</extref> of the Acts Interpretation Act 1908</citation> as set out in Schedule 2 of the Acts Interpretation Act 1924 continues in force despite the repeal of both of those Acts.</text>
            </para>
